metadata.name: Cellular Breakdown
metadata.description:
In Part I of IKAROS we begin our journey through a series of digital sculptures which together form a story of personal development. When viewed independently, each digital sculpture has its own unique teaching.

Cellular Breakdown: An exploration of our molecular environment that guides us with control.

Cellular Breakdown is a 1 minute, looping CG animation with custom audio track.

Resolution 1920x1080 pixel.

This NFT comes with a 55" display and custom framing with a seamless NFT playback. Our team will be in touch with the collector to establish delivery timeline and installation timeline.
